        <abstract>
            <para>The presented dataset includes herbarium specimens of lichens and mosses deposited at the Slovak National Museum - Natural History Museum in Bratislava, Slovakia (BRA) from the Slovak territory, from the period 1856 - 2008. The actual number of stored lichen and moss specimens in the museum is higher than this dataset showcases.</para>
        </abstract>
